      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE DOLLY (4) filled a minor placings again last time when second (22.91) at this track, making it three placings in a row. Has the ability and looks hard to top. LEARN TO FLY (5) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.20) at this track behind Singing Fox in a Maiden. Always well back but strong run home into the finish. Expected to be in this for a long way. SCARLET MOON (2) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and overdue for a win, having placed eight of 21 career runs. Deserves plenty of respect. WARRIOR WAH (3) was out of the money at this circuit when making debut but can do much better this time.",
